4 Results

extract_param <- function(model, parameter) {
  ci <- posterior_summary(model, variable = parameter)
  est <- sprintf("%.2f %.2f [%.2f;%.2f]", ci[,"Estimate"],ci[,"Est.Error"], ci[,"Q2.5"], ci[,"Q97.5"])
  est
}
